plowshare (2.0.1-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Rename plowshare4 -> plowshare source and binary
  * Remove the modules which now live in package plowshare-modules
  * patches/spelling*.patch:
    - Removed patches which are fixed upstream
  * patches/*:
    - Removed patches made irrelevant due to underlying changes in the code
  * debian/copyright:
    - Remove sections referring to deleted files
    - Point to new official source code location
  * debian/control:
    - Update description and homepage to reflect upstream reorganisation
    - Create a transitional dummy package for the rename
  * debian/watch:
    - Update to scan releases from the new upstream location

 -- Carl Suster <carl@contraflo.ws>  Sat, 4 Apr 2015 13:00:00 +1100

